name: Grounded under Supermoon
description: Grounded planes under the glowing Supermoon. Subtle animation of stillness.  It was a difficult year for humanity, things will improve, and it is up to us to return to a better normal. I joined hicetnunc to support a green NFT platform with my works.  Size: 1000x1000 pixels  /// I am a Budapest based artist working with early digital tools. I am a storyteller telling tales of capitalist realism. I research human vulnerability in our technology altered consciousness. MFA graduate student at Schoo
